@TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001
@TaskId = 1

### Root endpoint
GET {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/

### Create a task
POST {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Prepare software architecture diagram",
  "priority": "High",
  "dueDate": "2026-07-20"
}

### Retrieve all tasks
GET {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks

### Filter open tasks
GET {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks?status=open

### Search tasks
GET {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks?search=architecture

### Update a task
PUT {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "priority": "Medium",
  "dueDate": "2026-07-22"
}

### Toggle completion
PATCH {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}/toggle

### Delete a task
DELETE {{TaskFlow_TaskApi_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/{{TaskId}}
